-- Tirrenia Workers Called on Strike March 29 by Union Over Sale
-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 2012-03-17T17:44:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-17/tirrenia-workers-called-on-strike-march-29-by-union-over-sale.html
Tirrenia workers will strike on
March 29 after the European Commission “seemed to” block a
sale of the state-run ferry operator to Compagnia Italiana di
Navigazione Srl, labor union Federmar-Cisal said yesterday in a
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francesca Cinelli in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Ludden at 
 jludden@bloomberg.net  